text: Jacobus van der Vinden (1 October 1906 - 11 February 1972) was a Dutch gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Dutch male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
